  49:Middlewares/ST/threadx/common/src/tx_thread_relinquish.c **** /*    the list of threads ready at the same priority. If no other threads */
  50:Middlewares/ST/threadx/common/src/tx_thread_relinquish.c **** /*    of the same or higher priority are ready, this function simply      */
  51:Middlewares/ST/threadx/common/src/tx_thread_relinquish.c **** /*    returns.                                                            */
